Task 5:- Using Addition Assignment (+=) Operator:- In this approach we use Addition Assignment (+=) operator in which operator Sums up left and right operand values and then assigns the result to the left operand.
  let num1 = 15;
  let num2 = 10;
  // Equivalent to num1 = num1 + num2
  num1 += num2;
  console.log("Sum of the given number is :", num1);


Task 6:- Using the Subtract Assignment Operator:-
let a = 20; 
let b = 10; 

a -= b; 
console.log(a); // 10



